I finally finished making my scenario converter move all the objects 
around in "The Brag" to meet the new map.  Thankfully, I will only 
have to create 5 more objects in that scenario to accomodate the map 
(Assuming I don't run into problems with making my code delete objects 
AGAIN, I should have another update to my scenarios on Easter).  As 
promised, here's the code that manipulated 95% of the objects in that 
scenario.  Variable names come from the information they hold:
